<item>
            <title>[FELIX-1243] Change the default port for the OSGI HTTP Service from 8080 to 8181</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-1243</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I would like to change the default port for the OSGI HTTP Service by default as it clashes with the default port of tomcat 8080 etc.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12427981">FELIX-1243</key>
            <summary>Change the default port for the OSGI HTTP Service from 8080 to 8181</summary>
